release_note: Howdy! We ve completely revamped the underlying in app purchase infrastructure which should provide you with a more seamless experience with subscription renewals directly in the keyboard no more restoring purchases in the companion app! Along with a number of other improvements we hope you enjoy this latest version of TransKey. As always if you have any problems questions or concerns feel free to reach us directly at hello transkey.io.

Things got a little out of hand with 1.14.5 so this new patch is coming in to save the day! I appreciate all the emails letting me know the last update broke TransKey Premium for some users. As always don t hesitate to reach out at hello transkey.io if you have any questions or comments. Best Aleksander
We re on a streak! This time with yet another minor update containing bug fixes improvements and all that good stuff. Hope you re enjoying TransKey! Best Aleksander
Just some minor bug fixes and improvements coming your way. Happy new year! Best Aleksander

Another minor update to keep things rolling smoothly. If you were one of the affected users of a bug limiting your access to unlimited translations this should now be resolved. Thanks for your patience and please reach out to me at hello transkey.io with any further questions or comments! Best Aleksander

Some bug fixes coming in hot at the tail end of the year. As always if you encounter problems or have any questions at all feel free to email us at hello transkey.io. We d greatly appreciate it if you would drop a rating on the App Store too that helps other potential users discover TransKey. Happy holidays! Aleksander.

Another day another update version 1.14.0 of TransKey has finally arrived and includes a large number of behind the scenes improvements to ensure your experience is better than ever. Please consider leaving a review in the App Store if you find TransKey helpful it means a lot to us! As always if you have any problems at all please feel free to email us any time at hello alekapps.xyz. Aleksander.

We wanted to bring you some happy news amidst all the craziness TransKey 1.13.0 is here! This update includes improvements to how the translation engine powering your translations is chosen ensuring that even if one service is offline you can still translate your messages! It also allows you to manually set your preferred translation engine in the Options menu. We re continually working on making TransKey even better so that you never have to worry about texting someone in a foreign language. Please consider leaving a review in the App Store or sharing the app if you enjoy it we d really appreciate it! Should you run into any problems you can reach us any time at hello alekapps.xyz. Aleksander.

We re constantly working to improve TransKey so here s an update that fixes some bugs and makes sure your experience is better than ever! If you have any questions comments or would just like to chat I m all ears! Reach out on twitter at alekplay or by email at hello alekapps.xyz. Aleksander

They said it was impossible. They said it couldn t be done. They said translating the entire message was a myth and last sentence was the best we could hope for. Well TransKey 1.12.0 is here to prove them wrong! Starting today the entire message not just the last sentence will be translated allowing for even easier multi sentence cross language communication. And as if that wasn t enough we ve also made serious improvements to the Free Tier that we hope you ll love! In addition to scrapping the character based limit for 10 translations per day we ve also given you additional options for extra translations ranging from answering a survey to watching an ad. Cha ching. Should you run into any problems reach us any time at hello alekapps.xyz. And if you re enjoying TransKey please consider leaving a review in the App Store. I d really appreciate it! Aleksander.

Get ready to join the dark side with the new Dark Mode TransKey Keyboard! We ve also made improvements to ensure your experience with TransKey is smoother than ever before. Should you run into any problems reach us any time at hello alekapps.xyz. And if you re enjoying TransKey please consider leaving a review in the App Store. I d really appreciate it! Aleksander.

Things got a little out of hand with our previous update but fear not this hotfix is here to save the day. As always if you encounter any issues please email us at hello alekapps.xyz or reach out to me directly at alekplay on Twitter. Aleksander

Say hello to version 1.10.0 of TransKey which includes a number of changes to the onboarding making it even easier for new users to get started! In addition we ve also squashed a few bugs and made some improvements to ensure your experience with TransKey is smoother than ever. If you encounter any problems at all or just want to chat you can reach us by email at hello alekapps.xyz. And if you have a minute we d really appreciate if you left a short review in the App Store! Just a little fix coming in hot for you! This version of TransKey resolves an issue where some users would be kicked out of the companion app when it tried to verify your subscription status. Hopefully that s the last of em but if you run into any other bugs please let us know at hello alekapps.xyz. And psst it d mean the world to me if you would leave a quick review in the App Store! Aleksander.

Version 1.9.0 has landed and I hope you re as excited as I am because this update is jam packed with features you ll love! Here s just some of what I m most excited about: Switch languages even quicker by double tapping the one you want to select. Translate back and forth when using Detect Language by tapping the arrow between them. Plus a bunch of smaller improvements that s sure to make your experience with TransKey even smoother including but not limited to : Quickly access your most recently used languages by tapping the top of the languages screen. See your membership level in the Keyboard. Improved landscape layout. And as always we ve squashed our fair share of bugs. Speaking of if you run into any please let us know by contacting us at hello alekapps.xyz. And it d mean the world to me if you would leave a quick review in the App Store! Aleksander.

And we re back this time with more improvements to ensure your experience with TransKey is better than ever! If you run into any issues or have feedback please feel free to let me know by contacting me directly at hello alekapps.xyz. And it d mean the world to me if you could take a few seconds to leave a review in the App Store! Aleksander.

As much as we all love dark mode iOS 13 didn t come without issues. One of them prevented users on certain devices from switching away from the TransKey Keyboard whoops. This update fixes that by always giving you a keyboard switch button. We have a packed update schedule over the next few weeks so stay tuned for some cool new features and awesome improvements!

Some major minor improvements coming your way! We heard your reports about issues with TransKey Premium not being recognized in the keyboard and are happy to say that we ve fixed and improved the entire subscription process! As always if you stumble upon any issues please let me know by contacting me directly at hello alekapps.xyz. If you enjoy TransKey please consider leaving a review in the App Store!

Think you re a TransKey expert Think again! Check out the new Video Tutorials to learn power features such as how to translate multiple sentences! The Tutorials can be found by opening the TransKey Companion app and clicking Video Tutorials in the main menu. This update also includes a number of improvements to the on boarding making it easier than ever to get started with TransKey! As always if you stumble upon any issues please let me know by contacting me directly at hello alekapps.xyz. If you enjoy TransKey please consider leaving a review in the App Store!

Moder under the hood updates and bug fixes coming your way! If you have any issues suggestions or just general feedback please feel free to reach out to me directly at aleksander alekapps.xyz or alekplay on Twitter.

This update has yet another set of under the hood fixes that will ultimately allow me to build you a much better product. Exciting! It also includes a few bug fixes and user experience improvements so I hope you enjoy! If you happen to stumble upon any other bugs have any suggestions or just general comments please feel free to reach me directly at aleksander alekapps.xyz or alekplay on Twitter.

Just a few quick bug fixes coming your way! If you happen to stumble upon any other bugs have any suggestions or just general comments please feel free to reach me directly at aleksander alekapps.xyz or alekplay on Twitter. Enjoy!

This minor release introduces some major improvements to the user management system. While you won t notice many changes things are moving much smoother behind the scenes. One thing you ll love is that your TransKey Premium membership is now synchronized across all your devices. This means you can buy TransKey Premium once use it everywhere without having to Restore Purchases on the other devices! This is the second update in a series aimed at making using TransKey a smoother experience which will include confirming subscription status in the keyboard and much more. If you happen to stumble upon any bugs have any suggestions or just general comments please feel free to reach me directly at aleksander alekapps.xyz or alekplay on Twitter. Enjoy!

And we re back! This time we ve got some major behind the scenes improvements in store for you namely a new user management system. What this means for you is synchronization of your data and account across all your devices a better Referral Program signup flow and more. This is the first update in a series of updates aimed at making using TransKey a smoother experience which will include synchronization of Premium membership across devices confirming subscription status in the keyboard and much more. As always we ve squashed our fair share of bugs as well! If you happen to stumble upon any other bugs have any suggestions or just general comments please feel free to reach me directly at aleksander alekapps.xyz or alekplay on Twitter. Enjoy!

New version coming in hot with a few bug fixes and smaller improvements! As always if you notice any issues or have suggestions please reach out to me on Twitter alekplay or by email at aleksander alekapps.xyz. Thanks for using TransKey!

Two updates in one week We re on a roll! This one isn t as exciting but we ve still made some cool changes! If you run out of translations while using the keyboard you can now easily open the TransKey companion app to either upgrade or start referring friends! Did Full Access somehow turn off No worries jump straight to the settings screen from the keyboard! You referred some friends redeemed the Premium but oh no it s about to expire! You ll now get a helpful reminder when it s time to upgrade! The on boarding just got a little smarter and will direct you based on what you ve already completed! And as always you can count on the bugs being squish squashed. Did you find any other bugs have any suggestions or just general comments I d love to hear them! Reach me directly at alekplay on Twitter or by email at aleksander alekapps.xyz. Happy translating!

Welcome to Transkey! Today we re welcoming our Arabic speaking neighbors with a complete Arabic localization! Other than that I ve: Been hard at work squashing a few bugs. Reenabled the keyboard switcher on iPhone X devices to avoid that sticky situation when you re using an non optimized app and suddenly can t swap keyboards. If you find Transkey useful please consider sharing the app with your friends. You can simply tap Share straight from the keyboard. I d greatly appreciate it! And remember if you ever run out of translations I recommend upgrading to Transkey Premium for unlimited higher quality translations! For a small monthly fee you can unlock all the features Transkey has to offer and you d help support the future development of this app. If you find any bugs or have feature requests please feel free to email me through the Transkey app or tweet me alekplay!

The entire interface now bounces ever so pleasantly The app will guide you through the purchase process if you upgrade to Transkey Premium New unified interface for restoring purchases and refreshing subscription status That pesky app review prompt that appeared on the first launch is now gone Minor bug fixes and improvements If you find Transkey useful please consider sharing the app with your friends. You can simply tap Share straight from the keyboard. I d greatly appreciate it! Thank you to everyone for downloading Transkey! We ve got some cool new updates in this version we re excited to share with you so read on to find out more! The main app has been completely redesigned making it easier than ever to find the information you re looking for We ve moved away from offering individual translators and now provide a unified Premium subscription with unlimited translations powered by Google Translate A brand new onboarding flow makes it super easy to install and get started using Transkey Other improvements: The app and keyboard now supports the iPhone X The in keyboard share functionality now links directly to the App Store page You can now refresh your subscription directly from the keyboard If you enjoy Transkey it would mean a lot if you left a short review on the App Store and shared the app with others who may also like it. Thanks : Please reach out to me at alekplay if you notice any bugs or have feature requests! You can still use Transkey for free with the Yandex Translator engine for up to 90 characters per day as before. Microsoft Translator subscribers will retain their service indefinitely.

The new toolbar makes it easy to see how many characters you have left upgrade when you re running low and share TransKey with friends directly from the keyboard! No more monthly character limit on the free tier! Upgrade your translator engine straight from the App Store if you re running iOS 11! Other improvements: Speed up keyboard launch time Fix keyboard layout issues Squash some of the most common bugs If you enjoy the application it would mean a lot if you left a short review on the App Store. Thanks : Please reach out to me if you notice any bugs or have feature requests!

The Yandex Translator issues have been fixed the free tier should be stable again now! Please bear in mind that there is a limit on the number of translations per day month on the free tier. If you use TransKey a lot I suggest upgrading for unlimited better quality translations. You d also support the future development of this app : If you enjoy TransKey please consider leaving a review in the App Store. It d mean a lot! If you have any questions or comments please feel free to reach out to me at hello alekapps.xyz.

Only a few small changes and behind the scenes improvements this time! New app icon. Improved renewing subscription flow: a status page will appear if your subscription has expired while checking for updates in the main app. Bug fixes.

Choose your favorite translator! You can now easily switch between Google Translate Microsoft Translator and Yandex Translate in the main application. The translation engine you select will be used for all translations with the TransKey keyboard. Other improvements: Minor bug fixes throughout the application Optimizations for iPhone SE and iPhone 7 screen sizes Please reach out to me if you notice any bugs or have feature requests! If you enjoy the application it would mean a lot if you left a short review on the App Store. Thanks : Please note that TransKey is still free to use with Yandex Translate. For a small monthly fee you can upgrade to one of our premium translator engines Microsoft Translator or Google Translate. Please see description for further information.

New more structured design and layout making the app even easier to use! Optimizations for landscape orientation Minor bug fixes If you like TransKey I would appreciate if you left a short review. Thanks : Please reach out if you notice any bugs or have any feature requests!

TransKey was so popular Microsoft had to block it from making any further translations! Everything is up and running again now though sorry about that : If you think the app is useful please consider leaving a review in the App Store. Feel free to include any suggestions and feedback. Thank you! : This version includes a few minor additions and bug fixes: Added a button to swap the source and target language as requested by a user Made error messages more understandable Minor bug fixes

We ve surpassed 2 million translations per month! Thanks to everyone for downloading TransKey so far. Please consider leaving a review on the App Store if you like the app it d mean a lot : We ve got some exciting features coming up soon but for now just a few minor updates: Added iOS 10 compatibility. Updated translator api to avoid service interruption. Created a nicer pick to from language layout. Created a new on boarding experience. Fixed layout bug affecting keyboard labels. Fixed other minor bugs. Please feel free to reach out to me if you notice any bugs or have feature requests!
